{"tid":48190,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"梁特赴京述職 獲外交部長讚年輕有為愛國愛港","createTime":"2016-12-21T02:04:41.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-21T02:22:07.000Z","uid":48093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"fa4211a06f8d536d60ece3b62add5bab170998e5","tid":48190,"uid":48093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T02:04:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20161221/large/1482284940_ff56.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20161221%2Flarge%2F1482284940_ff56.jpg&h=d9d02a73&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n已宣佈不爭取連任的特首梁振英到北京進行任內最後一次述職，今早拜訪外交部，並與部長王毅會面。王毅讚揚梁振英年輕有為、愛國愛港，成為行政長官之後，雖然面對複雜的內外環境，仍堅定奉行一國兩制政策，為國家、為香港做了大量有益的工作，獻出自己的心血。<br />\n<br />\n王毅又指港澳辦和中聯辦都代表中央政府對梁振英充分肯定，而雖然外交部不主管香港事務，但仝人非常支持他，亦感謝他作出的貢獻。<br />\n梁振英表示，感謝王毅部長及外交部一直的支持，令香港在多方面都有良好發展，香港作為中國的國際化城市，有廣泛密切的對外關係，香港在外貿的經濟活動，體現高度國際化，現時在科技及文化，亦開展對外關係發展，而過程當中也為國家發展作出應有貢獻。"},{"pid":"749a5d97dcb8ce3bf2fa738ac4ef36eed77d325a","tid":48190,"uid":18320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T02:05:30.000Z","msg":"屌你老母留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76c5c5d66fec642119bff56d0e33c293ad3525e9","tid":48190,"uid":6267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T02:18:10.000Z","msg":"On9部部長"},{"pid":"252198cf0607b43f2f211dc214fdd3300df3de5f","tid":48190,"uid":33640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T02:19:38.000Z","msg":"唔講其他 邊到年輕呀大佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eeb321cb014dbba087f1e65150ce894a207250d2","tid":48190,"uid":10441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T02:22:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔講其他 邊到年輕呀大佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\"